  dialogPieces:
  - ID: Noah
    image: {fileID: 0}
    text: A ticket?
  - ID: Noah
    image: {fileID: 0}
    text: Advance Single.
  - ID: Noah
    image: {fileID: 0}
    text: "She was planning to leave\u2026"
  - ID: Noah
    image: {fileID: 0}
    text: "There\u2019s writing on the back\u2026"
  - ID: Noah
    image: {fileID: 0}
    text: "\u201CNot\u2026...I just\u2026\u201D"
  - ID: Noah
    image: {fileID: 0}
    text: What was she trying to say?
  - ID: Noah
    image: {fileID: 0}
    text: "\u2026It\u2019s only half a sentence."
  - ID: Noah
    image: {fileID: 0}
    text: If I piece it together, would it form a complete thought?
